-09T05:07:01.000Z","msg":"因為公司暗地係有壓力比到員工或者冇講出聲但人會有種無形壓力，你一戴口罩就好似比人標籤咁<br />\n<br />\n返緊工ge人應該會明，呢個時候真係突然冇曬人戴口罩。其實我地屌政府離地，同時都要緊貼現實情況。"},{"pid":"2f5e38814bf3ac171a3cdee20391e48df13675fe","tid":1640641,"uid":86218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"因為文革式批鬥已經黎到香港<br />\n戴口罩冇參與集結唔犯法<br />\n但係周街會有狗，休班狗，藍絲<br />\n捉住你，影你相，放上網，或者當面批鬥<br />\n個個都唔想成為事件中既主角"},{"pid":"5f8b5a46914d0c061f3a3b0ee5ae9c7c62438123","tid":1640641,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c805c81d087a26346c3d2a9435fa90b83ab0e2a6","tid":1640641,"uid":327300,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"你老母就犯法"},{"pid":"83807fd7c90abfaa3c0109878829b12e8ea83c6a","tid":1640641,"uid":111517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"屋企無口罩"},{"pid":"654b0b3f5bc10b74b5e6a0faac6c70dbecb8ecf1","tid":1640641,"uid":63400,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"因為暴徒唔係爭取五大訴求，而是破壞香港基建、堵路搶劫、縱火、殺人，所以花生友都要割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3739254aaa10d91b395fd726c527c3f31211a3f1","tid":1640641,"uid":31028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:09:32.000Z","msg":"多人戴味搞唔到囉！"},{"pid":"a66987ca36a9899d604ac96fa65e8ef42998fca2","tid":1640641,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"有幾可會出街消費<br />\n罷買罷食留係屋企<br />\n所以有幾可見到大部份人戴口罩出街"},{"pid":"9230efc44ad514915e40d41d80049a2424c927b4","tid":1640641,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:13:01.000Z","msg":"熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd8d6b0fd42ade96338759e9dc5951d5583d246","tid":1640641,"uid":320593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:13:56.000Z","ms